snippet.title: Palworld - Launch Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Palworld, with over 25 million players worldwide, is finally available on PS5!

Fight, farm, build and work alongside mysterious creatures called ""Pals"" in this completely new multiplayer, open world survival and crafting game!

#ps5 #ps5games #Palworld #pocketpair #stateofplay
